Product description

An EVA midsole and a soft EVA footbed allow this classic flip-flop to be incredibly lightweight and comfortably supportive. A subtle closure on its strap makes for a secure, adjustable fit while providing extra visual interest. Perfect for every beach on your summer getaway list.
